scene.message:
Dr. Nikolai: ...{nl}
Please reconsider!{nl}
Mr. Kandori!{waitkey}Stop the system and{nl}
atone for what{nl}
you have done!{waitkey}{ret}

Kandori: What nonsense.{nl}
It is all of foolish humanity{nl}
that must atone.{waitkey}I am merely its{nl}
guide.{waitkey}{ret}

Dr. Nikolai: Not even{nl}
the boy earlier deserved{nl}
to be sent to the void!{waitkey}{clearbox}What are you trying{nl}
to achieve by harming{nl}
children?!{waitkey}{ret}

Kandori: No one will{nl}
interfere...{wait_fr:94} not even{nl}
children.{wait_fr:60}{nl}
Judgment will fall soon.{waitkey}Early or late is merely{nl}
a matter of timing.{waitkey}{ret}

Kandori: I expected you.{nl}
So Takeda fell.{nl}
That man was weak.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: With me in the way,{nl}
a guy like him{nl}
was nothing!{waitkey}{clearbox}Surrender now and I'll{nl}
let you off with life{nl}
imprisonment!{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: A man who can't{nl}
admit defeat is just{nl}
unsightly.{waitkey}Won't you please{nl}
give yourself up?{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Ayase is busy —{nl}
stop wasting Ayase's time{nl}
with this!{waitkey}{nl}
Just come quietly,{nl}
okay?!{waitkey}{ret}

Kandori: Hm. You do love{nl}
to bark. Unfortunately,{nl}
I have no time for you.{waitkey}{clearbox}I have things to do...{nl}
Come, Dr. Nikolai.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: So this is{nl}
the DEVA System!{nl}
Kandori — what are you doing?!{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: ...This machine!{nl}
I... why...?{nl}
Why do I recognize it...?{waitkey}{ret}

Kandori's voice: Wha?!{nl}
This is...?!{wait_fr:94}{nl}
GAAAAHHH! My body?!{nl}
My body is...!!{waitkey}My body is fading?!{nl}
What is happening?!{waitkey}{ret}

Doctor's voice: Sir!{nl}
This is the end for{nl}
you as well!{waitkey}{clearbox}You deceived me in the{nl}
name of humanity and{nl}
caused all this — you must{nl}
pay for that!!{waitkey}{ret}

Doctor's voice: Children!{nl}
When we are reduced{nl}
to atoms, the system{nl}
will stop!{waitkey}When that happens,{nl}
the seal on the town{nl}
will break! Go now!{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Let's save him!{nl}
The old man shouldn't die{nl}
for someone like Kandori!{waitkey}{clearbox}Let's put that bastard{nl}
down with our own hands —{nl}
isn't that why we came?!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Wait. That old man{nl}
invented the system —{nl}
he wants to take{nl}
responsibility.{waitkey}{clearbox}We must respect{nl}
his wishes.{nl}
Besides, we don't know{nl}
how to stop it.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Y-yeah, yeah!{nl}
Listen to your elders —{nl}
let's get out of here!{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: {ctl07:1},{nl}
there's no time{nl}
to argue. Let's{nl}
save him!{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: {ctl07:1}!{nl}
This! This machine{nl}
can stop it!{waitkey}{clearbox}The red button is{nl}
emergency stop! Blue is{nl}
power boost! Red{nl}
can save him!{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: I don't know!{nl}
But I just know!{nl}
{ctl07:1}! Hurry!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: {ctl0f:1}, grow up.{nl}
Sometimes responsibility{nl}
has to be taken like this.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Hurry!{nl}
It's all over if he{nl}
dies — and there might{nl}
still be good ahead!{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Let's just retreat!{nl}
Pull back!{nl}
Your leader is asking!{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: That old man may{nl}
have people he loves...{nl}
You know what to do.{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Stop this already!{nl}
No more people dying...{nl}
Nobody wants to die, right?!{waitkey}{clearbox}Kandori can face justice.{nl}
Let's save him!{waitkey}{ret}

Kandori's voice: Ohh?!{nl}
My body — it's coming back!{nl}
So...{wait_fr:94} you're calling me!{waitkey}{ret}

Doctor's voice: Impossible?!{nl}
My work was perfect!{nl}
D-don't tell me —{nl}
it's HIM?!{waitkey}{ret}

Dark girl: {wait_fr:30}...{wait_fr:30}...{wait_fr:30}...{wait_fr:30}{nl}
I won't let Daddy die!{nl}
Let's go, Daddy!{waitkey}{ret}

Kandori's voice: Heh heh{nl}
heh... I won't die!{nl}
Lead me to your world{nl}
now!!{waitkey}{ret}

{color:2}Dr. Nikolai.{nl}
Genius scientist who{nl}
developed the D.V.A.{nl}
System.{color:0}{waitkey}{ret}

Red or blue — which{nl}
will you press?!{nl}
{ctl0e:16}{ret}

Maki: {ctl07:1}!{nl}
Where are you going?!{nl}
We have to do something!{waitkey}{ret}

"Dimension Variable{nl}
Accelerator System"{waitkey}{nl}
— the DEVA System.{nl}
A hologram.{waitkey}{ret}

COMP: Emergency!{nl}
Anomaly detected!{waitkey}Unknown virus confirmed{nl}
in hyperdimensional{nl}
shaft activation program!{waitkey}System shutdown impossible.{nl}
System shutdown impossible.{waitkey}Please perform manual{nl}
emergency shutdown.{nl}
Please perform manual{nl}
emergency shutdown.{waitkey}{ret}
